title: 'Boys and Girl - The Defensive Effort Debate; 4 Week Team, McCarthy Eval with The Athletic's Bob Sturm
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - The Defensive Effort Debate; 4 Week Team, McCarthy Eval with The Athletic's Bob Sturm
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby ask whether or not the Cowboys have an issue with effort and heart. Plus, Bob Sturm from The Athletic stops by to assess the Cowboys season through four games. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
